Try all the operators in the semver calculator page: https://semver.npmjs.com/
operators
^ allows changes that do not modify the left-most non zero element
~ allows patch changes if the minor version is specified. Allows minor versions if only the major version is 
specified. If the whole version number is specified (including patch and prerelease tags) then the last part is 
allowed to change
Pre-release tags:
$semver 1.2.3 -i prerelease --preid beta -> 1.2.4-beta.0
$semver 1.2.4-beta.0 -i prerelease -> 1.2.4-beta.1